title: (1969) Live at Woodstock - Jimi Hendrix (Blu-Ray Rip)
description:
This is the Blu-Ray rip of Gypsy Sun and Rainbows' Woodstock performance, recorded in 1969. The CD version of this album has weird phasing issues going on with Jimi's vocals, and is dynamically brickwalled. The Blu-Ray audio is much cleaner and, in my opinion, infinitely more desirable. The only pitfalls of this version is that it lacks track 3 of the CD version, "Hear My Train a Comin'."

Tracklist:

1. Introduction
2. Message of Love
4. Spanish Castle Magic
5. Red House
6. Lover Man
7. Foxy Lady
8. Jam Back at the House
9. Izabella
10. Fire
11. Voodoo Child (Slight Return)
12. Star Spangled Banner
13. Purple Haze
14. Woodstock Improvisation
15. Villanova Junction
16. Hey Joe
